# Shaky's Boba & Baguettes

A small Express + EJS web app showcasing products, search, registration, and a short customer survey.

## Features

- Browse product categories (Boba Milk Tea, Boba Fruit Tea, Baguettes, Snacks)  
- About page with shop info  
- Search products by name or category  
- Register with name and email  
- Complete a short survey and view results  
- Simple navigation header shared across pages

## Project structure

.
├── index.js                    # App entry point  
├── package.json                # Project metadata + dependencies  
├── readme                      # This file  
├── routes/  
│   └── main.js                 # Route handlers  
├── views/                      # EJS templates  
│   ├── index.ejs  
│   ├── about.ejs  
│   ├── search.ejs  
│   ├── search_result.ejs  
│   ├── register.ejs  
│   ├── registered.ejs  
│   ├── survey.ejs  
│   ├── survey_result.ejs  
│   └── partials/  
│       └── header.ejs  
└── public/  
    └── css/  
        └── stylesheet.css            # Application stylesheet

## Requirements

- Node.js (v14+ recommended)  
- npm

## Install

Open a terminal in the project folder and run:

```sh
npm install
```

## Run

Start the server:

```sh
node index.js
```

Open http://localhost:8000 in your browser.

## Routes

- /         — Home  
- /about    — About the shop  
- /search   — Search page  
- /register — Registration form  
- /survey   — Customer survey

## Notes

- Static assets are expected under public/ (CSS at public/css/main.css).  
- If navigation displays as a bulleted list, ensure the stylesheet is served (express.static) and that .nav-links has list-style removed in CSS.